    'ib.vs.0.t': 'Investment banking vs private equity',
    'ib.vs.0.d': 'Banking advises clients on deals and raising capital. Private equity invests its own fund and owns the companies it buys.',
    'ib.vs.1.t': 'Investment banking vs consulting',
    'ib.vs.1.d': 'Consulting advises on strategy and operations. Banking focuses on financial transactions and raising money.',
    'ib.vs.2.t': 'Investment banking vs corporate finance',
    'ib.vs.2.d': 'Corporate finance sits inside a company and manages its funding. Banking advises many companies from the outside.',
    'ib.vs.3.t': 'Investment banking vs asset management',
    'ib.vs.3.d': 'Asset management invests money for clients over time. Banking arranges one-off transactions and deals.',
    'ib.vs.4.t': 'Investment banking vs sales and trading',
    'ib.vs.4.d': 'Sales and trading buys and sells securities in the market. Banking advises on and structures corporate deals.',
