    'vc.skill.9': 'Judgement',
    'vc.skills.note': 'Financial modeling matters less here than in banking or private equity, since there are far fewer historical financials to model. What tends to separate strong junior investors is pattern recognition built from seeing many pitches, and the discipline to say no to most of them, since a fund typically only has capacity to back a small fraction of the companies it reviews.',
    'vc.route.0.t': 'Startup experience',
    'vc.route.0.d': 'Having worked at, or founded, a startup is highly valued.',
