    'act.roles.label': 'Roles',
    'act.roles.text': 'Each step up the ladder shifts the emphasis further from drafting documents to setting strategy and managing the client relationship. Most lawyers climb this ladder at the same firm, though moving firms or to a regulator at any level is common.',
    'act.roles.title': 'Roles in the competition law practice',
