    'bf.roles.text': 'Each step up the ladder shifts the emphasis further from drafting documentation to setting deal structure and managing the client relationship. Most lawyers climb this ladder at the same firm, though moving firms or to a bank at any level is common.',
    'bf.roles.title': 'Roles in the banking & finance practice',
