    'cma.day.label': 'A day in the life',
    'cma.day.p1': 'The day often starts with reviewing due diligence findings or the counterparty\'s comments on a draft purchase agreement. On quieter days, much of the time goes into working out warranties, indemnities and the other SPA provisions.',
    'cma.day.p2': 'A corporate/M&A lawyer often works on several transactions at once, each at a different stage. That requires switching quickly between matters and keeping track of dozens of open action points per deal.',
    'cma.day.p3': 'On completion day, the pace shifts entirely. The lawyer closes out the last conditions precedent, chases missing signatures, and coordinates with all parties on the exact moment of transfer.',
    'cma.day.title': 'A typical day for a junior lawyer',
    'cma.div.0.d': 'Acquisitions of listed companies, with the associated takeover rules.',
