    'cma.div.text': 'Corporate/M&A is broad, and most lawyers specialise within one of the sub-areas below.',
    'cma.div.title': 'The main sub-areas',
    'cma.do.0.d': 'Determining whether an acquisition is best structured as a share deal or an asset deal.',
