    'dr.emp.text': 'A selection of firms with a verified dispute resolution practice in the Netherlands. We only name firms whose practice group has been confirmed.',
    'dr.emp.text2': 'Alongside law firms, legal expense insurers also handle a large share of disputes in the Netherlands, often on behalf of individuals and SMEs.',
