    'ip.skill.8': 'Perseverance',
    'ip.skill.9': 'Strategic judgement',
    'ip.routes.label': 'Getting in',
    'ip.routes.title': 'How you get into intellectual property',
    'ip.routes.text': 'Most routes run through a law master\'s with a specialisation in IP law or private law, followed by an internship or traineeship at a firm. An affinity with technology or creative industries is a plus.',
    'ip.route.0.t': 'Master\'s in intellectual property or private law',
    'ip.route.0.d': 'The most direct route, with courses that tie directly into the practice.',
    'ip.route.1.t': 'Internship during the master\'s',
    'ip.route.1.d': 'Gaining practical experience at a firm before graduating.',
    'ip.route.2.t': 'Traineeship after graduating',
    'ip.route.2.d': 'Structured programmes in which you rotate through several practice groups.',
    'ip.route.3.t': 'A technical background or minor',
    'ip.route.3.d': 'Knowledge of STEM subjects is a strong asset for patent matters.',
    'ip.route.4.t': 'Student associations and committees',
    'ip.route.4.d': 'A board or committee year at a law student association builds network and experience.',
    'ip.route.5.t': 'Publishing in legal journals',
    'ip.route.5.d': 'A case note or article on IP law stands out in applications.',
    'ip.route.6.t': 'Work experience at a patent office',
    'ip.route.6.d': 'An internship at a patent office gives insight into the registration side of the field.',
    'ip.route.7.t': 'Networking with lawyers and alumni',
    'ip.route.7.d': 'Coffee chats and alumni contacts open many doors when applying.',
    'ip.prep.label': 'Preparation',
    'ip.prep.title': 'How to prepare as a student',
    'ip.prep.text': 'Preparation works best when it starts well before the application. Firms test not only legal knowledge, but also whether someone can grasp and explain technical subject matter clearly.',
    'ip.prep.0.t': 'Take courses in intellectual property',
    'ip.prep.0.d': 'Build a solid grounding in patent, trademark and copyright law.',
    'ip.prep.1.t': 'Read rulings on IP disputes',
    'ip.prep.1.d': 'Follow how judges assess and reason through an infringement case.',
    'ip.prep.2.t': 'Do a relevant internship',
    'ip.prep.2.d': 'Any internship at a firm or patent office strengthens your application.',
    'ip.prep.3.t': 'Practise interviews',
    'ip.prep.3.d': 'Prepare for questions on motivation, case studies and current affairs.',
    'ip.prep.4.t': 'Build a one-page CV',
    'ip.prep.4.d': 'Keep it clear and focused on relevant experience and results.',
    'ip.prep.5.t': 'Network early',
    'ip.prep.5.d': 'Reach out to lawyers and alumni before application rounds open.',
    'ip.prep.6.t': 'Follow developments in IP law',
    'ip.prep.6.d': 'Developments such as the Unified Patent Court follow each other quickly.',
    'ip.prep.7.t': 'Improve your English',
    'ip.prep.7.d': 'International patent proceedings and clients often require work in English.',
    'ip.vs.label': 'Compare',
    'ip.vs.title': 'Intellectual Property versus other practice areas',
    'ip.vs.text': 'These practice areas often overlap in the same matters, which is why students sometimes mix them up. The distinction mainly lies in which right is at the centre and who the counterparty is.',
    'ip.vs.0.t': 'Intellectual Property vs Commercial',
    'ip.vs.0.d': 'Commercial drafts the contract. Intellectual Property assesses which IP rights are being licensed or transferred within it.',
    'ip.vs.1.t': 'Intellectual Property vs Corporate/M&A',
    'ip.vs.1.d': 'Corporate/M&A guides the acquisition itself. Intellectual Property assesses the IP portfolio as part of due diligence.',
    'ip.vs.2.t': 'Intellectual Property vs Dispute Resolution',
    'ip.vs.2.d': 'Dispute Resolution conducts the proceeding once an IP dispute escalates to court. Intellectual Property handles the substantive IP strategy around it.',
    'ip.vs.3.t': 'Intellectual Property vs Antitrust, Competition & Trade',
    'ip.vs.3.d': 'Antitrust assesses whether a licence restricts competition. Intellectual Property assesses the validity and scope of the underlying right.',
    'ip.vs.4.t': 'Intellectual Property vs Tax',
    'ip.vs.4.d': 'Tax structures how royalty income from IP rights is treated for tax purposes. Intellectual Property protects and enforces the underlying right itself.',
    'ip.emp.label': 'Employers',
    'ip.emp.title': 'Firms with an IP practice in the Netherlands',
    'ip.emp.text': 'A selection of firms with a verified intellectual property practice in the Netherlands. We only name firms whose practice group has been confirmed.',
    'ip.emp.text2': 'Some of these firms focus entirely on IP, others combine it with other practice areas within a broader firm.',
    'ip.empcat.0': 'International firms',
    'ip.empcat.1': 'Boutique firms specialised in IP',
    'ip.vac.label': 'Vacancies',
    'ip.vac.title': 'Intellectual Property vacancies',
    'ip.vac.text': 'We only show real, current openings with a link to the employer. Internships, traineeships and lawyer roles appear here. In the meantime, browse all current vacancies.',
