    'ip.resx.0.t': 'Guide to drafting a patent application',
    'ip.resx.0.d': 'The structure of a patent application, step by step.',
    'ip.resx.1.t': 'Introduction to trademark law',
    'ip.resx.1.d': 'What trademark law involves and how registration works, explained briefly.',
    'ip.resx.2.t': 'Overview of the Unified Patent Court',
    'ip.resx.2.d': 'What the UPC means for European patent proceedings.',
    'ip.resx.3.t': 'Application guide for the legal profession',
    'ip.resx.3.d': 'How to write a strong motivation letter for a trainee position.',
    'ip.resx.4.t': 'List of firms with an IP practice',
    'ip.resx.4.d': 'A verified overview of firms offering this practice area.',
