    'cop.routes.label': 'Getting in',
    'cop.routes.title': 'How you get into operations consulting',
    'cop.routes.text': 'The routes are broad: alongside business and economics degrees, students from technical and logistics programmes also enter. An affinity with processes and figures is a plus.',
    'cop.route.0.t': 'A relevant university degree',
    'cop.route.0.d': 'Business, industrial engineering, econometrics or a technical programme.',
    'cop.route.1.t': 'Internship at an advisory or consulting firm',
    'cop.route.1.d': 'An internship is often the direct route to a starting offer.',
    'cop.route.2.t': 'A Lean or Six Sigma certification',
    'cop.route.2.d': 'A certification shows serious interest in process improvement.',
    'cop.route.3.t': 'Experience on a shop floor',
    'cop.route.3.d': 'Experience in production or logistics gives practical insight.',
    'cop.route.4.t': 'A board or committee year',
    'cop.route.4.d': 'A board year or committee shows leadership and initiative.',
    'cop.route.5.t': 'Case competitions',
    'cop.route.5.d': 'Taking part builds experience, network and visibility.',
    'cop.route.6.t': 'Networking on campus and at events',
    'cop.route.6.d': 'Consulting firms are active on campus and at events.',
    'cop.route.7.t': 'A sharp, concise CV',
    'cop.route.7.d': 'A clear one-page CV with results and experience.',
    'cop.prep.label': 'Preparation',
    'cop.prep.title': 'How to prepare as a student',
    'cop.prep.text': 'Preparation works best when it starts well before the application. Firms test your analysis and whether you can explain an improvement practically and persuasively.',
    'cop.prep.0.t': 'Practise cases',
    'cop.prep.0.d': 'Practise with operations and improvement cases.',
    'cop.prep.1.t': 'Learn the basics of Lean',
    'cop.prep.1.d': 'Understand the core concepts of process improvement.',
    'cop.prep.2.t': 'Do a relevant internship',
    'cop.prep.2.d': 'Any internship with process or analysis work strengthens your story.',
    'cop.prep.3.t': 'Practise mental maths',
    'cop.prep.3.d': 'Fast, accurate maths helps in cases.',
    'cop.prep.4.t': 'Build a one-page CV',
    'cop.prep.4.d': 'Keep it clear and focused on results and experience.',
    'cop.prep.5.t': 'Prepare your motivation',
    'cop.prep.5.d': 'Know why operations consulting, why this firm, and why you.',
    'cop.prep.6.t': 'Follow business news',
    'cop.prep.6.d': 'A feel for current operations questions helps in interviews.',
    'cop.prep.7.t': 'Network early',
    'cop.prep.7.d': 'Speak to consultants and alumni before application rounds open.',
    'cop.vs.label': 'Compare',
    'cop.vs.title': 'Operations versus other paths',
    'cop.vs.text': 'These paths sometimes overlap, which is why students mix them up. The distinction mainly lies in the type of work and how close you sit to execution.',
    'cop.vs.0.t': 'Operations vs Strategy Consulting',
    'cop.vs.0.d': 'Strategy decides where an organisation should go. Operations focuses on how the work gets done better and more efficiently.',
    'cop.vs.1.t': 'Operations vs Technology & Digital Consulting',
    'cop.vs.1.d': 'Technology & digital improves with technology as the engine. Operations improves the processes themselves, sometimes with and sometimes without new technology.',
    'cop.vs.2.t': 'Operations vs Data & Analytics',
    'cop.vs.2.d': 'Data & analytics builds models and insights. Operations uses those insights to concretely improve execution.',
    'cop.vs.3.t': 'Operations consulting vs an in-house operations role',
    'cop.vs.3.d': 'An in-house role works for a single organisation. As a consultant you work for many clients and see many different processes in a short time.',
    'cop.vs.4.t': 'Operations vs Financial & Deal Advisory',
    'cop.vs.4.d': 'Deal advisory assesses the financial side of a company. Operations improves execution, sometimes as part of an improvement programme after a deal.',
    'cop.emp.label': 'Employers',
    'cop.emp.title': 'Operations firms in the Netherlands',
    'cop.emp.text': 'A selection of firms with a strong operations practice and an office in the Netherlands. We only name firms whose practice is confirmed.',
    'cop.emp.text2': 'In addition, the strategy houses and the Big Four have their own operations units, and many operations specialists work in-house at a manufacturing or logistics company.',
    'cop.empcat.0': 'Strategy and management firms with an operations practice',
    'cop.empcat.1': 'Specialist and technology-driven operations firms',
    'cop.vac.label': 'Vacancies',
    'cop.vac.title': 'Operations vacancies',
    'cop.vac.text': 'We only show real, current openings with a link to the employer. Internships, traineeships and consultant roles appear here. In the meantime, browse all current vacancies.',
    'cop.vac.all': 'View all vacancies',
